Build
========
To build the system kernel (supervisor), issue

$ make

The kernel.elf file will be generated.

Directory Structure
======================

.
|
+- asm_core
|	Core architecture files
+- kernel
|	Main kernel C files
+- lds
|	Linker scripts for the kernel and external symbol definitions
+- lib
|	Core library files
+- periph
|	Peripheral drivers
+- syscalls
	System call implementations

Limitations
=============
- The kernel can not run standalone.

- There is no idle task.

- Exactly two processes are supported in the process queue.

- There is no priority scheduling.
